{"tid":1199660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［推]十一十二號，全民圍堵立法會阻止三讀須知","createTime":"2019-06-10T14:19:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T01:58:28.000Z","uid":70403,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"897d80534aa64880a591732603bdd3bc5c417dfc","tid":1199660,"uid":70403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:19:25.000Z","msg":"點解要反對修例，我唔再多講。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一百萬人上街，政府當港人契弟<br />\n十二號唔係簡單二讀 係直接想通過</span><br />\n香港人唔好再奢望和平遊行有用，<br />\n十二號早上十一時要集合立法會，<br />\n直接圍堵賣港賊 到時自有公論。<br />\n</span><br />\n到時十二號當日一定有佈防，等賣港賊順利入場，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">所以先至要十一號晚有勇士留守確保十二號順利圍堵。</span></strong></div></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以唔好再批評人衝擊暴力，<br />\n唔衝去圍堵的話班賊就會順利賣港</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w6ZEaYd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw6ZEaYd.png&h=c53ba653&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港全民罷工，警察們其實你地都係香港人！<br />\n香港警察們，希望你地當日盡香港人責任。<br />\n工作重要定家園重要？冇家園何來有工作？<br />\n你執意要做公安，我地香港人一定唔會留手。<br />\n你係都要助紂為虐，到時流血唔好怪香港人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eOpQhKf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeOpQhKf.png&h=afa9ea6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以下為當日議程，真憑實據。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cqNKm4U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcqNKm4U.png&h=d9c4aacc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">十一號晚留守的香港人請留意！<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n因為添馬公園係二十四小時開放，所以我地去訓教都完全冇問題，怕喺前線衝突嘅香港人可以留守公園，支援前方，相信到時半夜三點立法會門前必有清場，所以可以設置救護區或準備清水以備前線人員洗面。<br />\n以下為平面圖，方便大家熟路走位。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5MpMAEk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5MpMAEk.png&h=ac9d24ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RoTdZ50.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRoTdZ50.png&h=57e8f835&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後，請勿再責罵衝擊者。<br />\n俾人強姦，你會唔會只係嗌唔好？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">香港人，十一十二號圍堵賣港賊</div></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>歡迎留言建議仼何方法</strong></span><br />\n如下：<br />\n1. 留守策略，如果門口被清場，應該退去咩位置？<br />\n2. 幾點開始衝擊立法會？等十一點就衝定係啲賣港賊入哂去先衝入去圍堵？唔好再企係到等運到！講多次白行白企冇用架！唔方便衝就後排救人back up.<br />\n3. 主動出擊，一隊特定小隊去捕捉議員好，捉林奠又好。停車場等？有客到就立即通知香港人。<br />\n4. 全民傳媒記者，我知香港人中意拎手機影相，到時見到有緊急事請放低電話。<br />\n5. 日常支援物資，清水，扔雞蛋，大聲公等？<br />\n6. 要有人做天文台聯繫，大聲公通知前線後方。<br />\n7. 交通路面又可以做咩啲？可以呼籲參與罷工嘅公司團體揸車到金鐘馬路塞滿車，唔止罷工，你地可以做更多。<br />\n8. 最重要，點衝好？要利用物資，可以用滅火筒噴鷹犬，扔雞蛋。"},{"pid":"4ea0920276029f171c9b554364677d59032d1d91","tid":1199660,"uid":70403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:29:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6dbefa7957a3609631c7c9a1f49982896eb5d46b","tid":1199660,"uid":70403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:30:15.000Z","msg":"到時香港人盡量著長衫長褲運動鞋，方便走動。"},{"pid":"f9c3bccb6f19bff2852545c26c75f56a9dfa092c","tid":1199660,"uid":70403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:40:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/BSSpYPs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBSSpYPs.gif&h=2ca456a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ace094526c1015e0733818de9c2f99b3a48c936","tid":1199660,"uid":8290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006c5520ac33f389ab9ef65cabf81f3bf2a04faf","tid":1199660,"uid":70403,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:42:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">十二號唔好等放工先嚟啊！<br />\n到時乜都完架啦</span></strong>"},{"pid":"3aab2fec6731b799742a4421bbdba1c8f9898d67","tid":1199660,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:43:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4988f9cd55062bf09e957326af881da90129075c","tid":1199660,"uid":70403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:46:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5fed61ebc4d7d50dd3a6d525a3cd051df610a534","tid":1199660,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:47:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sQip62x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsQip62x.png&h=3b7750c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b6d69276648ae9c265a52848e0d0ebe5182a31b","tid":1199660,"uid":70403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fed61ebc4d7d50dd3a6d525a3cd051df610a534","tid":1199660,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:47:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sQip62x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsQip62x.png&h=3b7750c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:49:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cf2522417f3496264d543b1c99090ad4fa9a02d","tid":1199660,"uid":70403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ace094526c1015e0733818de9c2f99b3a48c936","tid":1199660,"uid":8290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:49:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddbe091b659f9d8cca3afcef453c1260dbaa5f3d","tid":1199660,"uid":70403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3aab2fec6731b799742a4421bbdba1c8f9898d67","tid":1199660,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"